			<div class="text-left lap-text-left tab-text-left mob-text-left">
				<div class="description ">
                	<p>Step into the legend of the world’s most iconic spy and immerse yourself in high-stakes espionage through intense combat, stealth-driven infiltration, and cutting-edge gadgetry. Powered by <a href="/geforce/graphics-cards/50-series/">NVIDIA GeForce RTX™ 50 Series</a>, <em>007 First Light</em> lets you explore its globe-spanning world with stunning path-traced** visuals and AI-powered <a href="/geforce/news/dlss-4-5-dynamic-multi-frame-generation-6x-mode-released/">NVIDIA DLSS 4.5</a>** with Dynamic Multi Frame Generation and Ray Reconstruction.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>For a limited time, get <em>007 First Light</em> with the purchase of a qualifying NVIDIA GeForce RTX™ 5090, 5080, 5070 Ti, 5070, 5060 Ti desktop system or graphics card, or laptop with a GeForce RTX 5090 Laptop GPU, RTX 5080 Laptop GPU, RTX 5070 Ti Laptop GPU, RTX 5070 Laptop GPU, or RTX 5060 Laptop GPU. Technology varies by GPU.</p>
